current.name: Non-Surgical Face Mask
current.description: Help your customers and employees stay safe when you give these custom face masks. Made of 100% polyester, they are certified for prolonged contact with the skin and are also washable so they can be used over and over. Please note that this mask is not medical grade and will come with either a black or white elastic strap.

current.name: Keychain CPR Mask
current.description: Add the compact Keychain CPR Mask to your set of keys and be prepared in case of an emergency! Packaged in a small red and white pouch, the mouth to mouth mask can be quickly retrieved by opening the velcro closure.

current.name: Christel 7-piece personal care kit
current.description: Christel 7-piece personal care kit.Make sure you always look your best. This set includes a mirror, tweezers, a nail clipper, a toe nail clipper, a pair of scissors, a nail file and a cuticle tool. The set comes in a handy nylon pouch.Microfibre nylon.

current.name: Blank Disposable Non-Surgical Face Mask
current.description: Designed to keep your employees and customers safe, these ear-loop face masks are a welcomed gift. They are made with three layers of non-woven fabric, including a high-density filter layer that protects the mouth and face from liquid, airborne particles, allergens, and dust. Please note that these come blank and are not medical grade. Masks are CE approved in accordance with EU Directive on Medical Devices 93/42 / EEC, Annex VII, Class 1 Type II & Type IIR approved in accordance with EN 14683.

current.name: Face Shield
current.description: Protect your employees with these safeguard face shields that cover the forehead and chin. Theyâ€™re made with an adjustable elastic head strap and a cushioned foam bar that ensures the right fit and hours of comfort. To make it easy on you, the face shields come pre-assembled and ready to hand out. Before the first use, clean the face masks with a soft cloth, mild soap/detergent, and water. Please note that these masks are not medical grade or personal protective equipment (PPE). Do not use them in the presence of a high-intensity heat source or flammable gas.

current.name: Carry-On Kit
current.description: Carry-On Kit. Zip-top resalable pouch for TSA-friendly travel. Includes 3 80mL refillable bottles, 1 80mL refillable spray bottle and mini funnel. Bottles and funnel packed in polybag, comes seperatly from pouch. Decoration not available on components. PVC.

current.name: First Aid Set In Pouch
current.description: First Aid Sets are always an appreciated gift that could prove essential in unexpected situations. Show your customers and employees you care by adding these promotional first aid sets to your next campaign. This set includes a pouch with one front pocket, one black zipped main compartment and a belt loop on backside of pouch. It contains a triangle bandage, pbt bandage, alcohol pad, plasters, scissors, pin and tape.
